"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:11.3.1.9\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">11.3.1.9</span> 標題：罷特（bath）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： bath)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:26\">1KI 7:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:38\">1KI 7:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:9\">2CH 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:9\">2CH 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:5\">2CH 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:10\">ISA 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:10\">EZK 45:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:11\">EZK 45:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:11\">EZK 45:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:14\">EZK 45:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:14\">EZK 45:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:14\">EZK 45:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:14\">EZK 45:14</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <em>Bath</em> （罷特）是乾量「伊法」的對應液量。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:26\">1KI 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:5\">2CH 4:5</a> ：在這兩節經文中，銅海的容量是用「罷特」來度量的。學者對於「罷特」的具體大小並未達成一致意見，因此各譯本在翻譯<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:26\">1KI 7:26</a> 所記銅海的容量時，差異非常的大，比如80,000升（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> 直譯）、40,000升（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 直譯）、11,000加侖（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 直譯）、10,000加侖（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直譯），等等。請注意，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:26\">1KI 7:26</a> 所記容量為2,000罷特，而<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:5\">2CH 4:5</a> 作3,000罷特。翻譯者不應該試圖統一這兩個數值。另參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.3.2 聖殿：海(Temple: sea, tank)&lt;REALIA:4.3.2&gt;</a> 中的討論。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:10\">ISA 5:10</a> ：參上文<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">11.3.1.4 賀梅珥（homer）&lt;REALIA:11.3.1.4&gt;</a> 關於「賀梅珥」的註解。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:10\">EZK 45:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:11\">EZK 45:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:11\">EZK 45:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:14\">EZK 45:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:14\">EZK 45:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:14\">EZK 45:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:14\">EZK 45:14</a> ：這幾節經文指出伊法和罷特是一樣的，都是一賀梅珥的十分之一。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
